  "title": "Forklift Operator",
  "description": "<p></p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will perform picking and packing duties, maintain accurate stock counts, prepare inventory and logistics reports, and follow standard operating procedures to support daily logistics operations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Pick and pack orders accurately to meet delivery requirements</li><li>Count and verify stock quantities to maintain inventory accuracy</li><li>Prepare and update basic inventory and logistics reports to support operational tracking</li><li>Follow standard operating procedures (SOPs) to ensure consistent and safe logistics processes</li><li>Operate forklifts safely and efficiently within daily logistics tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a valid Forklift License issued within the last 3 years</li></ul>",
